span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0cfM4t5ns_text","label":"gg0cfM4t5ns_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I brought the bowl to Max's next vet appointment.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Dr. Rodriguez was amazed. <strong>\"18 months without a single episode? Show me how this works.\"</strong></span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I demonstrated Max's new drinking pattern.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>\"Brilliant. It's mechanically preventing volume shock. The stomach never gets overwhelmed.\"</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoKfS5q2bg_text","label":"ggoKfS5q2bg_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">\"Sarah, in 15 years of emergency medicine, this is the first time I've seen <strong>complete prevention</strong> instead of just risk reduction.\"</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>The transformation went beyond physical:</strong></span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Max started playing after drinking instead of standing frozen with discomfort.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Her anxiety around water disappeared completely.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I could leave her with friends without writing frantic instruction lists.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">We could hike without me carrying emergency bloat medication.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>Most importantly: I finally sleep through the night.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBWEHPkZ7E_tex